.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BOTH-RESERVES-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-both-reserves-max \- FEAT-2397 channel where our_reserve + their_reserve is highest
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-both-reserves-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-both-reserves-max verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2397).
